# Frontend App Architecture

## 라우팅 (`App.tsx`)

| Path | Layout | Page / Guard |
|------|--------|--------------|
| `/` | MainLayout | HomePage |
| `/membership` | MainLayout | MembershipPage |
| `/payment/complete` | MainLayout | PaymentCompletePage |
| `/memo/:id` | MainLayout | MemoPage |
| `/admin/login` | AdminLayout | AdminLoginPage |
| `/admin` | AdminLayout → AdminProtectedRoute | AdminDashboardPage |

**MainLayout**: `useAuthInit`, `useUsageInit`, `useMemoInit` + LeftSidebar, Navbar, AuthModal, AppToaster, ThemeToggle, `<Outlet />`

**AdminLayout**: `checkAdminAccess()` → blocked면 `AdminBlockedPage` (라우터 밖), allowed면 `AdminLayoutContent` + `useAdminAuthInit`

## Zustand Stores

| Store | Persist | 서버 데이터 | 핵심 |
|-------|---------|------------|------|
| `authStore` | Yes (`auth-storage`) | user/token | `login`, `logout` |
| `adminAuthStore` | Yes (`admin-auth-storage`) | admin/token | 별도 JWT |
| `authModalStore` | No | — | `mode: login\|signup\|null` |
| `usageStore` | **No** | UsageData | `setUsage`, `resetToGuest`, formatters |
| `memoStore` | **No** | Memo[] | CRUD, `ensureMemoLoaded`, `saveMemoContent` (직렬 큐) |
| `memoPlaybackStore` | No | — | `currentTime`, `isPlaying`, `resetPlayback` |
| `wordSelectionStore` | No | — | `memoId`, `selectedIndices` |
| `themeStore` | Yes | — | `light\|dark`, `applyTheme` |
| `sidebarStore` | Yes | — | `isOpen`, width 288 |
| `rightSidebarStore` | Yes | — | `isOpen`, `width` 260–520 |

**persist 금지**: memo, usage, transcript, admin stats

## Init Hooks (`MainLayout` / `AdminLayoutContent`)

| Hook | 트리거 | 동작 |
|------|--------|------|
| `useAuthInit` | mount | token → `fetchMe` → login / logout |
| `useUsageInit` | token 변경 | `fetchUsage` → setUsage / resetToGuest |
| `useMemoInit` | user 변경 | `loadMemos` / setMemos([]) |
| `useAdminAuthInit` | mount | admin token → `fetchAdminMe` |

## API Layer

### `lib/api.ts` — base `/api`, Bearer from `authStore`

| Function | Endpoint |
|----------|----------|
| `register`, `login`, `fetchMe` | `/auth/*` |
| `fetchUsage` | `GET /usage/me` |
| `uploadAudio` | `POST /uploads/audio` (XHR + progress) |
| `startTranscription` | `POST /transcripts` |
| `fetchTranscript`, `fetchUpload` | GET |
| `fetchMemos`, `fetchMemo`, `renameMemo`, `saveMemoWords`, `saveMemoContent`, `deleteMemo` | `/memos/*` |
| `generateWordAiNote` | `POST /memos/:id/words/:wordIndex/ai-note` |
| `preparePayment`, `completePayment` | `/payments/*` |
| `getUploadAudioUrl`, `resolveMemoAudioUrl` | URL 헬퍼 |

공유 타입: `AuthResponse`, `UploadResponse`, `TranscriptResponse`, `MemoResponse`, `UsageData`, `CreditPackId`

### `lib/adminApi.ts` — base `/api/admin`

`adminLogin`, `fetchAdminMe`, `fetchAdminStats`, `checkAdminAccess`

## 페이지 책임

### HomePage
- 드래그·드롭·파일 선택 업로드 (audio/video)
- 파이프라인: `uploadAudio` → `startTranscription` → `loadMemos` → `navigate(/memo/:id)`
- `ProcessStep`: idle → uploading → transcribing → creating-memo → complete
- `PROGRESS`: 33 → 66 → 90 → 100
- 비로그인 → `openLogin()`, 전사 실패 시 Cloudinary 업로드됨 toast description
- `UsageProgress` + 최근 메모 3개

### MemoPage
- `ensureMemoLoaded(id)`, 404 → `/`
- `useMemoTranscript` — words/segments/audio hydrate
- 제목 수정, 삭제 confirm → `/`
- `MemoWaveformPlayer` + `memoPlaybackStore`
- `MemoTranscriptEditor` — 단어 클릭 seek
- `MemoPageShell` + `WordNotePanel`
- 언마운트: `clearSelection`, `resetPlayback`

### MembershipPage
- 6개 크레딧 팩 UI (데스크톱 테이블 / 모바일 카드)
- `usePlanPayment` → PortOne V2

### PaymentCompletePage
- `?paymentId` → `completePayment` → `setUsage`

### Admin
- `AdminLoginPage` → `/admin`
- `AdminDashboardPage` — StatCard, recharts, RecentUsers/Payments
- `AdminBlockedPage` — IP 차단 + clientIp

## 주요 컴포넌트

| Component | 역할 |
|-----------|------|
| `MemoWaveformPlayer` | `@arraypress/waveform-player`, seek, volume |
| `MemoTranscriptEditor` | 단어 chip, context menu, selection |
| `WordNotePanel` | 단어 노트 편집, AI 버튼, virtual list |
| `AuthModal` | login/signup 폼 |
| `LeftSidebar` | memo 목록, MemoList |
| `Navbar` | 로그인/로그아웃, 멤버십 링크 |

## Utils

- `utils/transcriptToMemo.ts` — transcript content → memo words/segments 변환·동기화
- `utils/memoExport.ts` — 메모보내기

